Package org.knime.base.node.preproc.filter.column

Contains the filter column node which can be used the extract certain columns from the input data table.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataColumnSpecFilterNodeDialogPane
    This is the dialog for the column filter.
    DataColumnSpecFilterNodeFactory
    The factory for the column filter node.
    DataColumnSpecFilterNodeModel
    The model for the column filter which extracts certain columns from the input DataTable using a list of columns to exclude.

Package org.knime.base.node.preproc.filter.column Description

Contains the filter column node which can be used the extract certain columns from the input data table. Furthermore, this node's dialog has to be used in order to make the column selection. See DataColumnSpecFilterNodeFactory on how to instantiate this node. For convince, the DataColumnSpecFilterNodeDialogPane can be used also with other nodes to perform a column selection.
